snippet.title: Box Kid Adventures | Release Date Trailer | PC
snippet.description:
Box Kid Adventures is coming to PC on 28th January 2020.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1217870/Box_Kid_Adventures/

Box Kid Adventures is a dynamic, top-down puzzle game.
You play as Box Kid – a toy made of cardboard – going through various levels, full of nasty enemies and brain challenging puzzles.

#BoxKidAdventures #puzzle #indiegames #videogames #Robbo #cute
